{"tid":1634812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裝修會喪失民意","createTime":"2019-10-07T10:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T15:00:12.000Z","uid":316665,"like":6,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"efcde093c9e6cc56d9505e87ac184b6cc4277b4e","tid":1634812,"uid":316665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:09:38.000Z","msg":"破壞富臨美心交通橙只會損失民意<br />\n只有經濟制裁會得到民意<br />\n我認為以家勇武做多左<br />\n急功近利無用<br />\n場仗要起碼打多一年<br />\n睇下大陸仲托緊市<br />\n仲有排打"},{"pid":"0d9724117bb6b165022b7ff332e939d82d0970ed","tid":1634812,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:10:14.000Z","msg":"bye"},{"pid":"c971254ecf05fa16b0f0bd5816d7fca06c92502b","tid":1634812,"uid":73959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:11:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">⚠連登️五毛分化警告⚠️<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有堆ac<ins>專係撩交嗌</ins><br />\n目的想阻止理性討論<br />\n先起底 後無視 再block</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">請謹記初心<br />\n槍口一致對準</span><span style=\"color: red;\">政府、中共、黑警</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">和勇絕不割蓆 一切以大局為重</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed66b7bb6b83f1af5fe13df0fd5a160c0fec2c40","tid":1634812,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cd1817b42d68c6343758a2012bdd1c2d905f3e","tid":1634812,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:11:19.000Z","msg":"【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文見此：<br />\n<br />\n【行動】緊急！要突破分化！我有三個錦囊俾大家一定要繼續做落去！（分析長文）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1634772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1634772</a>"},{"pid":"287a42251c220e91050329013eefa3539a9ba66e","tid":1634812,"uid":141879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"今晚見"},{"pid":"844cb5bbf52b75138a84c69c2e3bbd5d0f1e5838","tid":1634812,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2b7c99451a7517c0de651660f73b8a40ac79b6c8","tid":1634812,"uid":42502,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"悶唔悶 blocked"},{"pid":"a9e9c819b8f6d3de33b401dbd66326bcc72ac838","tid":1634812,"uid":249883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:15:32.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"4b17f51340b1f9aa7dd02ce67959cbafa08c76fc","tid":1634812,"uid":316665,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a9e9c819b8f6d3de33b